channel.title: SabsabiOnline
channel.description:
[center][img]http://i.imgur.com/MkhF6zd.png[/img][/center]
[left][b][size=24pt]Introduction[/size][/b][/left] The server that was once the biggest of them all, where friendships, enemies and drama was made. My and countless of others childhood memories was formed here, the best time I have ever had during my time with RSPS. We've failed multiple of times, but it's time we take our stand once again and show the world of RSPS, why we are the greatest and always will remain the greatest. The only thing that can stop us, is ourself. The server will be a donation-free server, we will not take donations UNLESS it's absolutely needed, I don't believe in p2p / p2w, all features should be free to every player that enjoys the game. Back in 2010, SabsabiOnline was the leading RSPS with 3 worlds, each world maxing a total of 500+ players (world 2 would max 800 at a time).

item.title: SabsabiOnline
item.dc:creator: @Chronicles Chronicles
item.description:
@Chronicles wrote:

It’s been a busy week with xmas and everything. I managed to write a equipment dumper (dumps the equip slots). We read the data from a text file (dont laugh plz). But yeah, this should ensure that no items equip the wrong way.

for people who needs this.

	public boolean isWieldable() {
		try {
			if (actions == null)
				return false;
			String menu = actions[1].toLowerCase();
			return (menu.equals("wear") || menu.equals("wield") || menu
					.equals("equip"));
		} catch (Exception e) {
			return false;
		}
	}

	public static void dumpEquipments() {
		try {
			FileWriter fw = new FileWriter("equips.txt");
			for (int j = 0; j < totalItems; j++) {
				ItemDef item = ItemDef.forID(j);
				if (item == null || item.name == null || !item.isWieldable())
					continue;
				String name = item.name.toLowerCase();
				int slot = 3;
				if (name.contains("body") || name.contains("torso")
						|| name.contains("robe top")
						|| name.contains("robetop") || name.contains("jacket")
						|| name.contains("tunic") || name.contains("shirt")
						|| name.contains("top") || name.contains("blouse")
						|| name.contains("gown") || name.contains("hauberk"))
					slot = 4;
				else if (name.contains("shield") || name.contains("defender")
						|| name.contains("book"))
					slot = 5;
				else if (name.contains("boots"))
					slot = 10;
				else if (name.contains("cape") || name.contains("backpack")
						|| name.contains("apparatus")
						|| name.equalsIgnoreCase("eye patch")
						|| name.contains("accumulator")
						|| name.contains("cloak"))
					slot = 1;
				else if (name.contains("hat") || name.contains("helm")
						|| name.contains("mask") || name.contains("bandana")
						|| name.contains("cavalier") || name.contains("beret")
						|| name.contains("coif") || name.contains("wreath")
						|| name.contains("hood") || name.contains("sallet")
						|| name.contains("cowl"))
					slot = 0;
				else if (name.contains("legs") || name.contains("skirt")
						|| name.contains("bottoms") || name.contains("pants")
						|| name.contains("leggin") || name.contains("shorts")
						|| name.contains("tasset") || name.contains("chaps")
						|| name.contains("druidic robe")
						|| name.contains("cuisse"))
					slot = 7;
				else if (name.contains("amulet") || name.contains("scarf")
						|| name.contains("necklace"))
					slot = 2;
				else if (name.contains("ring"))
					slot = 12;
				else if (name.contains("glove") || name.contains("vambrace"))
					slot = 9;
				else if (name.contains("arrow") || name.contains("bolt"))
					slot = 13;
				fw.write(j + " " + slot + "\r\n");
			}
			fw.close();
		} catch (IOException ioe) {
			ioe.printStackTrace();
		}
	}
